Start Your Claim Today.
With Allstate, it's easier than ever to file a claim or track an existing one. If you have questions, you can contact your agent
 or call 1-800-ALLSTATE
 for 24/7 assistance. You can also count on the Allstate claims team to be there and help guide you throughout the claims process.

File a claim
Track a claim



Quick Access
Need to locate a claim owner? Simply enter the claim number to get in touch.
Go




Get Help Along The Way.

Allstate agents are committed to providing you with quality, personalized attention and can help answer any questions you may have about the claims process. 



Talk to an agent today



