Auto



Home, Condo, Renters



Disaster



Life



Flood







Motorcycle ClaimsPlease note that these are processed the same as our auto claims.
Auto Glass ClaimsThese are processed separately from our auto claims.



When Disaster Strikes.

If your community is affected by a severe weather event, Allstate's National Catastrophe Team (NCT) can help. Qualified claims professionals and mobile claims centers come to your area to help assist you with the disaster claims process.


See how Allstate helps in a disaster



Stay Protected From Fraud.

Insurance fraud is on the rise. Do you know what to look out for? See what you can do to help protect yourself on the road and at home. Plus, learn more about Allstate's innovative approach to fighting fraud every day.  


Learn about fraud protection



  

